description: (Enterprise Tier Only) Commands to manage job execution instances of Azure Spring Apps service.

commands.name: az spring job execution instance list
commands.summary: List all instances of the job execution.
commands.syntax:
az spring job execution instance list --execution
                                      --job
                                      --resource-group
                                      --service
examples: az spring job execution instance list --job job-name --execution job-execution-name -s MyService -g MyResourceGroup
